data.description: Just in time for the New Year! this beautiful home is back on the market and ready for immediate sale. Amazing five bedroom, plus loft, three bath home. Over three thousand square feet, on a quiet cul-de-sac, with a great water view. Features include a saltwater pool. complete hurricane protection, and a two car garage. This lovely home has been completely updated, marble flooring downstairs and wood floors upstairs. No HOA screening required. A rated schools. Close to schools, shopping, and major roads.
